.git
.github
.gitignore
terraform
**/.terraform
*.tfstate*

# Secrets & local data (DATABASE_URL is injected at runtime)
.env
**/.env
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal

# Misc
*.log
.DS_Store
README.md
